            <h4> Hobbies </h4>
                <p> These are my hobbies here. People have said I have a wide range of interests. My most prominent one is gaming. I really enjoy console and PC gaming alike, whether it's casual or competitive.
                    I have played a wide variety of games, ranging from retro ones on an emulator to modern multiplayer ones. My favourite genres are action-adventure open world games, I really enjoy exploring these fictional landscapes, getting stronger and lost in the flow of the game.
                    I also enjoy party games when I'm playing with my friends, but don't mind playing more competitively from time to time. I would like to get into more shooters again but there's no good ones currently and I do kinda get bored of them.
                    Regardless some of my all-time favourite games include the following. Click the button to get more explanation. </p>

